title: Can anyone help me identify this one
content:
Hey all,

Can anyone here help me with a name on this typeface, or one similiar? I have been seeing it all over the places now, but i don’t know what it is called. It is so fancy and i am so curious. Hehe.

Regards, and thanks for your help.

comments.content:
I’m pretty sure this is an old Letraset font called Stripes. I don’t know of any digital versions.

- Lex

I only know of this eroded / distressed version of the font:

[http://www.dafont.com/killed-dj.font](http://web.archive.org/web/20081023162942/http:/www.dafont.com/killed-dj.font "http://www.dafont.com/killed-dj.font")

hope that helps,

That helps alot, any input is much appreciated.  
Thanks.
